   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Improving indigenous peoples&#x2019; access to justice and development through strategic monitoring</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Overall objective: Indigenous peoples&#x2019; access to justice and development is monitored and enhanced at a global scale Specific objective: 1. Indigenous peoples&#x2019; access to justice and development is enhanced in a number of pilot countries in Africa, Asia and Latin America, through community-based monitoring and reporting of violations of indigenous peoples&#x2019; rights, as enshrined in the UN Declaration on the Rights of Indigenous Peoples, ILO Convention No. 169 and other relevant instruments 2. Indigenous peoples&#x2019; rights and aspirations for development are included in the post-2015 development agenda</narrative>
  </description>
